# 🎮 Tic Tac Toe Game

A simple, interactive **Tic Tac Toe** game built with **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript**. Play against another person on the same computer!

## 🛠️ Features
- 2-player mode
- Visual win detection 
- Reset game button
- Responsive and clean UI

## 💻 Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (Vanilla)

## 🧠 How It Works
- Players take turns to mark X or O in the 3×3 grid.
- The game checks for winning conditions after every move.
- The game can be restarted at any time with the "Reset" button.


